        "type": "regex",
        "pattern": "\\bwaka_tok_[A-Za-z0-9]{10,50}\\b",
        "message": "WakaTime access token detected in source code. Access tokens provide authenticated access to WakaTime API services including coding statistics, time tracking data, and user profiles. Exposing these tokens allows unauthorized access to personal coding activity and sensitive productivity data. Store tokens securely using environment variables or secure credential management.",
